column5: Nice video! Interesting techniques, shallow water and no floats for crappie. What type of structure is that? If you dont mind me asking
Sorry, I couldn't watch if with that Horrible  Music
Beds around clumps of emerging lily pads

Steve, you get into some great fish and you are a great young fisherman. Myself,I would like to hear commentary instead of the music. Like what you are looking for,tips,baits,setups and so on, during your vid. Your obvisouly not worried about where you are fishing. And no, I don,t care where.   JMO

What Misfish said!!!  15-20 years ago my pants were lower than yours and my chain wallet was to the knees... and our hip hop and rap was better.  What you got going on though is the fishing.  Solid craps again.
Cool fishin, but I too had to kill it early due to music..
Nice fish. Nothing wrong with the music lol, just throw her on mute if it bothers you.

I just picked a song on the playlist that was the same length as the video haha.  Musical tastes will always vary, but thanks for the input.  And yes the pants issue comes out to play again.  I've always been bad for it, but especially since losing 60lbs and not fully updating the wardrobe.  Ah well. haha
Nice fish Steve! And a great video!  I too found some Crappies yesterday, it was a beauty day to be out!
Slabs. Was a great day for it!
Song was too much for me as well  but once it was muted no complaints with that kind of fishing!
another good day for ya steve...thanks for sharing...cant wait for friday to roll round...crappie hunting for me too.
Nice fishing dude! Good job on the big slabs!  LTF
sweet slabs dude! Did you get a new boat? That sure doesn't look like the Legend to me
loved the music , its you , loved the fishing even more . Keep it up Bro
